methodology:
AGGI data was downloaded in .csv format from http://www.esrl.noaa.gov/gmd/aggi/. CFC 11 and CFC 12 were binned, other halogenated gases are represented by the "15 minor" category.  

The data used are from January 1, 1979 to December 31, 2013.

The data was accessed on September 15, 2014.
